                                    <div class="col-xs-12" style='margin-top:25px!important;'>
                                            <p  style=''>Dear Sir,</p>
                                            <p  style=''>Assalamu Alaikum, </p>
                                            <span  style=''>This is to inform you that we are submitting the following original document against L/C No. <span style='font-weight:bold;'><span t-field="o.lc_num2" /> dated <span t-field="o.lc_date2" /></span> of <span style='font-weight:bold;'><span t-field="o.lc_bank_name" />,<span t-field="o.lc_bank_brunch" />,<field name="lc_bank_address" /></span> amounting to <span style='font-weight:bold;'><span t-field="o.currency_symbol" /><span t-field="o.ordered_products_total_amount" /></span> in favour of our Company.</span>
                                    </div>
