                                        <p style='margin-left:30px;'>4.  Delivery Challan</p>                                    
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-xs-6" >
                                        <p><span t-field='o.c4' />  Copy (Original)</p> 
                                    </div>
    
                                    <div class="col-xs-6" >
                                        <p style='margin-left:30px;'>5.  Truck Challan</p>                                    
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-xs-6" >
                                        <p><span t-field='o.c5' />  Copies (Original)</p>
                                    </div>
    
                                    <div class="col-xs-6" >
                                        <p style='margin-left:30px;'>6.  Certificate of Origin</p>                                    
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-xs-6" >
                                        <p><span t-field='o.c6' />  Copies (Original)</p>
                                    </div>
    
                                    <div class="col-xs-6" >
                                        <p style='margin-left:30px;'>7.  VAT-||</p>                                    
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-xs-6" >
                                        <p><span t-field='o.c7' />  Copy (Original)</p>
                                    </div>
    
                                    <div class="col-xs-6" >
                                        <p style='margin-left:30px;'>8.  BTMA Certificate</p>                                    
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-xs-6" >
                                        <p><span t-field='o.c8' />  Copy (Original)</p>
                                    </div>
    
                                    <div class="col-xs-6" >
                                        <p style='margin-left:30px;'>9.  Beneficiary Certificate</p>                                    
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-xs-6" >
                                        <p><span t-field='o.c9' />  Copies (Original)</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-xs-12">
                                        <p style=''>
                                             We would therefore request you to kindly arrange for negotiating th documents at the earliest and also request you to kindly transfer <span style='font-weight:bold;' t-field="o.transfer_per" />% of the L/C Proceeds to tour F/C Account No. <span style='font-weight:bold;' t-field="o.fc_account_no" />
                                        </p>
            
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
            
                                        <p style=''>
                                            Thanking You.
                                        </p>
                                        <p style=''>
                                            Sincerely yours,
                                        </p>
            
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
            
                                        <p style='margin-top:20px;font-weight:bold;'>
                                            Authorized Signature
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
